    {
      "id": "TZeCzQOjqbwIHzstId043",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -117.01314090897529,
      "y": 1.4494675440190008,
      "width": 742.1598510742188,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "az",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 17710357,
      "version": 835,
      "versionNonce": 13418747,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783255986538,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "从三角形最后一层开始看，下沉到底的最优解就是自身值\n看相邻的上一层：如果要找下沉到底的最优解，就是找自身值 + min(dp[j], dp[j+1])\n其中，自身值 = triangle[i][j]，表示第 i 行第 j 列的值\n使用 dp[j] 来记录从第 i 行第 j 个位置下沉到低的最优解\n自底向上逐层更新的状态转移方程：dp[j] = triangle[i][j] + min(dp[j], dp[j+1])",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "从三角形最后一层开始看，下沉到底的最优解就是自身值\n看相邻的上一层：如果要找下沉到底的最优解，就是找自身值 + min(dp[j], dp[j+1])\n其中，自身值 = triangle[i][j]，表示第 i 行第 j 列的值\n使用 dp[j] 来记录从第 i 行第 j 个位置下沉到低的最优解\n自底向上逐层更新的状态转移方程：dp[j] = triangle[i][j] + min(dp[j], dp[j+1])",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hPeB_AEk3vObtVttnnVTj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -421.42605723512656,
      "y": 1.4494677413909187,
      "width": 119.91993713378906,
